### Integration Tests (macOS CI)
- `kqueue::integration::tcp_listener` - Accept connections
- `kqueue::integration::tcp_stream` - Read/write on stream
- `kqueue::integration::many_connections` - 100+ concurrent FDs
- `kqueue::integration::with_io_driver` - Full IoDriver integration

### Stress Tests
- `kqueue::stress::rapid_register_deregister` - Fast churn
